title: MISTERIX 2 BETA V1.0 LAUNCHER BY ZEB89
description:

Misterix 2 for GTA San Andreas.

A modification which adds the widely discussed myths and legends into the game the player to seek and sometimes kill.

This mod makes all the myths/monsters in the game come true.



MISTERIX 2 aims to greatly enhance, improve and extend the original version of the mod released back in 2007.

We will include:

- More myths to find

- Highly improved versions of the classic myths such as Bigfoot & Leatherface

- Some faster and much more lethal monsters

- More challenging ways to kill monsters

- Improved character models and new animations

- Sometimes, more complex conditions for triggering myths

- No problems caused by saving/loading the game

- Overall highly improved code

- New sounds and music to add immersion

- Much more!
